    "chapter_title": {
      "ar": "بَابُ أَنَّ الْحُجَّةَ لَا تَقُومُ لِلَّهِ عَلَى خَلْقِهِ إِلَّا بِإِمَامٍ",
      "en": "Chapter 4 – The Divine Authority cannot be established for Allah<sup>azwj</sup> upon His<sup>azwj</sup> creatures except by an Imam<sup>asws</sup>"
    },
    "gradings": [
